    "body": "Would like to add the following:\r\n\r\n<!--StartFragment-->\r\n\r\nSlug | Description\r\n-- | --\r\n`eip-number-nft` | An EIP Number NFT must be burned and linked to the Pull Request. EIP Editors may claim and burn NFTs themselves at no cost.\r\n`eip-number-nft-multisig` | Identical to `eip-number-nft`, except there is a multisig of EIP editors.\r\n`eip-number-nft-on-sidechain` | Identical to `eip-number-nft`, except on a sidechain (since we don't need all of the security that Ethereum provides).\r\n`eip-number-nft-multisig-on-sidechain` | Identical to `eip-number-nft-on-sidechain`, except there is a multisig of EIP editors.\r\n\r\n<!--EndFragment-->",
